tag_list: "Andre Crom & Chi Thanh" "Freedom Call feat. Jinadu" "dubspeeka Remix" "Off Recordings"
title: Andre Crom & Chi Thanh - Freedom Call feat. Jinadu (dubspeeka Remix) [Off Recordings]
description:
Following up on their original release, we are happy to present 3 excellent remixes for Andre Crom & Chi Thanh’s “Freedom Call”, featuring the anthemix vocals of Jinadu.

dubspeeka, known from a streak of amazing originals and remixes on Drumcode, LNOE and other labels, makes his OFF debut with a deep dub techno remix in his signature style, chopping up the vocal in a hypnotic way.

Musumeci, who established himself with a small but very characteristic number of tracks on Connaisseur, Bedrock and his own “Engrave LTD” label, delivers 2 remix versions; both in his trademark minimalistic and timeless production style.

Finally, Melokolektiv, one of OFF’s new core acts, deliver an interpretation that is both functional and epic, based on a latin flavoured groove.
